headline.main: CHINESE MINES SINK 2 TOKYO TRANSPORTS; Sea Guerrillas Score Off Fukien -- Japanese Bomb Kienow

lead_paragraph: CHUNGKING, China, Nov. 1 (AP) -- Chinese "sea guerrillas" operating along the Fukien Province coast have destroyed two Japanese transports, the Central News Agency reported today.
